lf. Our basic service includes installing it to your domain and hosting. So please order our basic service and we will install it for you.', 'array(\r\n        \"id\" 		 => \"Rose-Windpersonal\",\r\n        \"url\" 		 => \"https://kits.artstudioworks.net/rose-wind/landing/\",\r\n        \"purchase\" 	 => \"/downloads/rose-wind-personal-blog-theme/\",\r\n        \"responsive\" => \"yes\",\r\n        \"type\"       => \"wordpress\",\r\n        \"thumb\"      => \"\"\r\n    ),'),
