(47, 'Adra - Modern & Creative Theme', 'Adra-babiato-@TingTung', 'adramodern-creative', 'https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-admin/post.php?post=6901&action=edit', '/downloads/adra-modern-creative-theme/', 'https://closecrowds.com/themes/?theme=adramodern-creative', 'https://elements.envato.com/adra-modern-creative-elementor-template-kit-QAY8C9P', 'https://adra.stylewish.org/', 19, 'Agency,Business,Corporate,Creative,Elementor,Flow,Fluent,Modern,Multipurpose,Professional,Responsive,Template Kit,Wave,Wordpress,', '', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1muipk_R09XLYGAbXQHDrb69e0dxypM71/view?usp=sharing', '<p>Adra: A Modern &amp; Creative Theme for Elementor with bold typography and vivid colors. Ideal for professionals, creatives, artisans &amp; agencies who need a creative one page portfolio website &ndash; all in a few clicks. Of course Adra for Elementor has been fully optimized with for all devices and has a slick Responsive design that will scale fluidly to seamlessly display your content across a wide range of today&rsquo;s portable devices.</p>\r\n<p>With it&rsquo;s super simple Drag &amp; Drop Page builder approach Elementor does all the hard work for you to allow you to focus on what&rsquo;s most important to you &ndash; your content.</p>\r\n<p>With the Global Theme Styles you can rest assured the design is consistent across all pages. It&apos;s also super easy to adjust the styling at once with these controls.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Responsive Design</li>\r\n    <li>Drag &amp; Drop Page Building with Elementor</li>\r\n    <li>Works with Elementor Free and Elementor Pro</li>\r\n    <li>Header and footer block included</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>Instruction</h2>\r\n<h3>How to Use Themes:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Install and Activate the \"Envato Elements\" plugin from Plugins &gt; Add New in WordPress</li>\r\n 	<li>Download your themes file and Do not unzip</li>\r\n 	<li>In WordPress, go to Elements &gt; I